A minimalistic rss reader, written in perl/tk.

1. Copy example-config.yaml to config.yaml and edit.
2. Copy example-feeds.yaml to feeds.yaml and edit.
3. Use dbsetup.pl to create sqlite database file.
4. Use fetch.pl to download feeds. Put it to crontab or while true loop
   to fetch regularly.
5. Use rss.pl to read the feeds. Navigate by mouse or arrow+tab keys.
   Double-click or enter to open article in external browser.
